OL,3,CDad overcomes catastrophic brain
OL,4,Cinjury after double crash
OL,6,FA father who suffered a catastrophic
OL,7,Fbrain injury after a being hit by two
OL,8,Fcars in the same crash says giving up
OL,9,Fwas never an option.
OL,11,FMark Fardon was hit by a minibus on
OL,12,FManchester Road, in Rochdale, while
OL,13,Fdriving to work on a motorbike in 2015.
OL,15,FWhile he was in the middle of the road
OL,16,Fand already unconscious, another car
OL,17,Fhit him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
