OL,3,CDad overcomes catastrophic brain
OL,4,Cinjury after double crash
OL,6,FThe dad suffered a catastrophic brain
OL,7,Finjury and was in a coma for five
OL,8,Fweeks. His loved ones were told he had
OL,9,Fvery little chance of pulling through.
OL,11,FMark said: "The lady, who was in the
OL,12,Fpassenger seat in the minivan that hit
OL,13,Fme, went to get blanket from a care
OL,14,Fhome to cover me up. When she got
OL,15,Fback, I was 50 yards further down the
OL,16,Froad.
OL,18,F"I think they got told they have a 5%
OL,19,Fchance of survival, at best."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
