OL,6,FMark eventually woke up from a coma
OL,7,Fbut found he could not walk or talk,
OL,8,Fand had temporarily lost almost all of
OL,9,Fhis memory.
OL,11,FAfter years of physiotherapy and
OL,12,Fpsychology set up by Fletchers
OL,13,FSolicitors, he is now able to walk and
OL,14,Ftalk again.
OL,16,FHe said: "I didn't know my own name. I
OL,17,Fdidn't know I had a daughter. I didn't
OL,18,Fknow I had children. I didn't know
OL,19,Fwhere I lived, didn't know who my
OL,20,Ffriends were. I didn't know anything.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
