OL,6,F"I had to have physiotherapy two or
OL,7,Fthree times a week, and psychology
OL,8,Fonce a week for a long time, for years.
OL,10,F"It was frustrating, so much so that
OL,11,Fsometimes I didn't want to wake up."
OL,13,FMark wanted to express his thanks to
OL,14,Fhis friends and the people who worked
OL,15,Fwith him during his lengthy recovery.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
