OL,6,FHe said: "When I came out of hospital,
OL,7,Fmy biggest support was my support
OL,8,Fworker Steph. Without a doubt, she
OL,9,Fhelped put me back together and I've
OL,10,Fmade a personal friend for the rest of
OL,11,Fmy life.
OL,13,F"But my best friend, Gary, and his
OL,14,Fwife, Sharon - without them, God knows
OL,15,Fwhere I'd be. I can't thank them
OL,16,Fenough.
OL,18,F"I'm so grateful. I can never thank
OL,19,Fthe people who helped me enough. I've
OL,20,Ftried, but you can never do enough.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
