OL,6,FOne of the main motivations for Mark
OL,7,Fto keep fighting during his recovery
OL,8,Fwas his daughter Lexi, now 15.
OL,10,F"I wanted my daughter to get her dad
OL,11,Fback", he said. "The Mark that woke up
OL,12,Fwasn't Mark."
OL,14,FMark is a huge fan of the Foo
OL,15,FFighters, and has loved their music
OL,16,Flong before the crash and ever since.
OL,18,FThe band has been a constant
OL,19,Fthroughout his life. He says he would
OL,20,Flove nothing more than to go and see
OL,21,Fthem at Anfield in 2026.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
