OL,6,FHe said: "Music is a very powerful
OL,7,Fthing. I can't tell you how much it's
OL,8,Faided me with my recovery, and driving
OL,9,Fme on to see them live again.
OL,11,F"I first saw them play live in America
OL,12,Fin 1995. I arranged my holidays
OL,13,Fwhenever they were playing live,
OL,14,Fwherever they were in the world.
OL,16,F"They've announced two shows at
OL,17,FAnfield for next year and I can't get
OL,18,Ftickets. I would love to go."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
