OL,3,CDad overcomes catastrophic brain
OL,4,Cinjury after double crash
OL,6,FMark's crash has given him a renewed
OL,7,Fappreciation for life, despite still
OL,8,Fhaving to deal with some of the damage
OL,9,Fcaused by the incident.
OL,11,FHe said: "If I want to do something.
OL,12,FI'll do it now, because I might not be
OL,13,Fhere tomorrow.
OL,15,F"No one knows better than me that you
OL,16,Fnever know what's round the corner."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
