OL,3,CDad overcomes catastrophic brain
OL,4,Cinjury after double crash
OL,6,FHe can no longer taste or smell, and
OL,7,Fis not allowed to drive or run. But he
OL,8,Fstill makes the most of life, and
OL,9,Fwants to encourage others who have
OL,10,Fsuffered similar injuries to keep
OL,11,Fgoing.
OL,13,FHe added: "As hard as it is, it's
OL,14,Fincredibly hard, impossibly hard to
OL,15,Fexplain how hard it is.
OL,17,F"But you can't give up, you have to
OL,18,Fget better. What's the choice?"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
